\id 2JN - Baibal Kathoung New Testament
\h 2 JAWHAN
\toc1 2 JAWHAN
\toc2 2 Jawhan
\toc3 2 Jn
\mt1 2 Jawhan
\mt2 (The Second Epistle of John)
\c 1
\s1 Lawk karouknae
\p 
\v 1 Kacue e kai ni, a rawi e bawinu hoi a canaw hah ca na patawn. Lawkkatang dawk ka lungpataw teh, kai ni dueng laipalah lawkkatang ka panuek e naw pueng nihai lung na pataw awh.
\v 2 Bangkongtetpawiteh, lawkkatang teh maimouh thung kaawm niteh maimouh koe pou ao han.
\v 3 Pa Cathut koehoi, Pa e Capa Bawipa Jisuh Khrih koehoi, lungmanae, pahrennae hoi roumnae teh lawkkatang hoi lungpatawnae lahoi nangmouh koe awm lawiseh.
\s1 Lawkkatang hoi lungkâpatawnae
\p 
\v 4 Maimae na pa koehoi kâpoelawk coe awh e patetlah na canaw tami tangawn ni lawkkatang dawk a hring awh tie ka hmu navah ka konawm poung.
\v 5 Hatdawkvah bawinu, kâpoelawk katha hah ka thut hoeh, ahmaloe hoi maimouh koe kaawm tangcoung e kâpoelawk, buet touh hoi buet touh lungkâpataw awh sei telah ka kâhei.
\v 6 Lungkâpataw tie teh Bawipa e kâpoelawknaw tarawinae hah doeh. Hote kâpoelawknaw teh ahmaloe hoi na thai awh tangcoung e patetlah lungpatawnae dawk hringnae hah doeh.
\v 7 Jisuh Khrih teh tami coungnae lahoi a tho yaw ma ka tet e tami het talaivan moi a tâco toe. Hot patet e taminaw teh dumyennae hoi kakawi e tami a tho dawkvah khrihkaphawk doeh.
\v 8 Maimouh teh ma ni tawk e pahmat laipalah tawkphu kakueplah hmu awh han.
\v 9 Khrih e cangkhainae dawk kaawm hoeh e tami teh Cathut panuek hoeh. Khrih e cangkhainae dawk kaawm e tami teh Pa hoi Capa hah a panue.
\v 10 Hete cangkhainae tawn laipalah apipatet hai nangmouh koe tho pawiteh na im dawk luen sak a hanh, dawn awh hanh.
\v 11 Bangkongtetpawiteh, hot patetlah e tami hah na dawn pawiteh, ahnie hawihoehnae dawk na ka bawk e lah na o.
\s1 Lawkthuinae
\p 
\v 12 Nangmouh koe dei hane kawi moi ka tawn rah ei, cahna dawk cahang hoi thut hane hlakvah, nangmouh koe ka pai vaiteh buet touh hoi buet touh lunghawinae a kuep nahanlah nangmouh koe ka tho teh, nangmouh hoi lawk kapan awh han tie doeh ka ngaihnawn teh ka ngaihawi.
\v 13 Rawilah kaawm e na nawngha e a canaw ni kut na man awh. 
